---
import { siteConfig } from "../config";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- FONT -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <title>FAQ</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white text-gray-800">

    <section class="px-6 sm:px-10 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 overflow-x-hidden">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-20 items-start">

        <!-- LEFT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">

          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Frequently Asked Questions.
          </h2>

          <div
            class="w-[75px] h-[5px] mt-2 rounded-full"
            style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
          ></div>

          <p class="text-gray-500 mt-5 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
            Common questions about services, workflow, and project process.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 w-full min-w-0">

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl 
                      p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12
                      shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300
                      w-full max-w-full">

            <div class="space-y-10 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">

              <!-- 1 -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. What services do you offer?</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                  <li>Graphic design (posters, banners, social media, thumbnails)</li>
                  <li>Photo editing and retouching</li>
                  <li>Video editing (YouTube, Instagram, cinematic)</li>
                  <li>Motion graphics and visual content</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 2 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. How can I start a project?</h2>
                <p>
                  Contact me via website or email with your requirements. I will share pricing, timeline, and next steps.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- 3 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. What information do you need?</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                  <li>Project details or idea</li>
                  <li>Reference examples</li>
                  <li>Required size or platform</li>
                  <li>Deadline</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 4 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. How much do you charge?</h2>
                <p>
                  Pricing depends on type, complexity, and time. Custom quotes are provided per project.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- 5 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Do you take advance payment?</h2>
                <p>Yes, advance payment may be required to confirm your project.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 6 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. How many revisions are included?</h2>
                <p>Limited revisions are included. Extra revisions may be charged.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 7 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">7. How long does a project take?</h2>
                <p>Small tasks: 1–2 days. Larger projects vary based on scope.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 8 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">8. What file formats will I receive?</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                  <li>JPG / PNG</li>
                  <li>MP4 / MOV</li>
                  <li>Source files (if included)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 9 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">9. Will I get full rights?</h2>
                <p>Yes, after full payment. Work may be used in portfolio unless agreed.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 10 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">10. Do you offer refunds?</h2>
                <p>Generally non-refundable once work starts.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 11 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">11. Urgent projects?</h2>
                <p>Yes, depending on availability. Extra charges may apply.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 12 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">12. Long-term work?</h2>
                <p>Yes, I’m open to ongoing collaborations.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 13 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">13. What if I don’t like the design?</h2>
                <p>Revisions will be provided based on feedback.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 14 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">14. Communication?</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                  <li>Email</li>
                  <li>Messaging platforms (if agreed)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 15 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">15. Client content?</h2>
                <p>Clients must ensure they have rights to provided content.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 16 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">16. Portfolio?</h2>
                <p>Yes, available on this website.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 17 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">17. Custom styles?</h2>
                <p>All designs are tailored to your needs.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 18 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">18. After completion?</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                  <li>Files delivered</li>
                  <li>Minor support provided</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 19 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">19. International clients?</h2>
                <p>Yes, I work globally.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- 20 -->
              <div class="border-t pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">20. Contact?</h2>
                <p>{siteConfig.social.email}</p>
              </div>

            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

  </body>
</html>
